    "description": "体验一名认证叉车司机的超凡技巧与勇敢！<br><br>一个鲜为人知的秘密是，许多叉车司机其实都是长颈鹿，而现在你也能亲身体验仓库长颈鹿的惊险生活！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/ac74bb06559fef3cef40f330156ecf64.poster.avif?t=1770237435\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/ac74bb06559fef3cef40f330156ecf64.webm?t=1770237435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/ac74bb06559fef3cef40f330156ecf64.mp4?t=1770237435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轮子还是蹄子！</h2><br>《Extreme Forklifting 3》是一款基于关卡的第三人称驾驶游戏，在使用蹄子时还包含一些轻度的平台跳跃元素。<br>使用你的叉车将托盘运送到目的地，搭建桥梁并穿越危险障碍，在仓库里，一切都有可能发生！<br>当变成长颈鹿形态时，你可以在叉车之间切换，跳过裂缝，并操作传送带和拉杆等设备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/7ce0f933a424daac0ae79ab99b598034.poster.avif?t=1770237435\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/7ce0f933a424daac0ae79ab99b598034.webm?t=1770237435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/7ce0f933a424daac0ae79ab99b598034.mp4?t=1770237435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种车辆！</h2><br>驾驶灵活的三轮电动叉车；而对于更重的货物，可以使用四轮丙烷或柴油叉车。<br>当这些都不可用时，你就只能依靠老伙计——手动搬运车了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/49cad3bf5bf9f4bf35677747b328f80d.poster.avif?t=1770237435\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/49cad3bf5bf9f4bf35677747b328f80d.webm?t=1770237435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172570/extras/49cad3bf5bf9f4bf35677747b328f80d.mp4?t=1770237435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最新的仓库时尚！</h2><br>自定义你的叉车、手动搬运车，甚至打造你的梦想长颈鹿！<br>用贴纸、扰流板或酷炫轮毂来个性化你的托盘搬运利器。给你的长颈鹿围上一条与砖墙完美搭配的时尚围巾吧！<br><br>《Extreme Forklifting 3》，那款你从未知道自己想要的游戏！",
